Text:
@honzas7, unfortunately you cannot make the MP4 files play with subtitles on the PS3, you would have to convert it to an AVCHD on DVD or USB stick. Videohelp.com has plenty or links on how to do this. 

Video quality is superb like any other SecretMyth release but I have to agree that the audio was slighly off in this release. Easily fixable with YAMB or MKVMerge. A delay of minus -300ms is enough to bring it into perfect sync. 
For those that say it is fine then I'm glad you enjoyed it.
